                The Nisab serves as the minimum wealth for Zakat obligations. To
                qualify, check the market value of gold or silver. It's 87.48
                grams of gold or 612.36 grams of silver. If you have this amount
                or its cash equivalent, Zakat is obligatory.
              </p>
