                <span class="text-green-600">Step 2:</span> Assess Your Assets
              </h6><br />
              <p class="font-roboto">
                For a precise Zakat calculation, evaluate all your assets like
                cash, savings, investments, jewelry, and business assets. Don't
                include non-eligible assets like your main home or personal
                items.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

